{"legislative_session": "119", "identifier": "HCONRES 61", "title": "Directing the President, pursuant to section 5(c) of the War Powers Resolution, to remove United States Armed Forces from hostilities with presidentially designated terrorist organizations in the Western Hemisphere.", "from_organization": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["resolution"], "subject": [], "abstracts": [], "other_titles": [], "other_identifiers": [{"identifier": "ocd-bill-us-119-hconres61"}], "actions": [{"description": "Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.", "date": "2025-12-17T23:02:03+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "On agreeing to the resolution Failed by the Yeas and Nays: 210 - 216 (Roll no. 345).", "date": "2025-12-17T23:01:56+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Failed of passage/not agreed to in House On agreeing to the resolution Failed by the Yeas and Nays: 210 - 216 (Roll no. 345).", "date": "2025-12-17T23:01:56+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Considered as unfinished business. (consideration: CR H6004-6005)", "date": "2025-12-17T22:31:22+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "POSTPONED PROCEEDINGS - At the conclusion of debate on H. Con. Res. 61, the Chair put the question on agreeing to the resolution and by voice vote, announced the noes had prevailed. Mr. Meeks demanded the yeas and nays and the Chair postponed further proceedings until a time to be announced.", "date": "2025-12-17T18:46:23+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "The previous question was ordered pursuant to